sessions.description:
A large urban school district in Southern California, USA will share their implementation of badging for 3 purposes:
Recognizing students’ college, career, and life readiness;
Building community badging partnerships with local non-profit organizations;
Collecting data for a grant with a consortium of 10 organizations.
Come hear about these various use cases all using a common digital badging platform and how digital badging has brought this community together to celebrate and recognize learning.
